00:00:35.650 --> 00:00:45.690
It's simply the argument
that for every major ideology

00:00:45.690 --> 00:00:48.540
associated with the
change of a city,

00:00:48.540 --> 00:00:53.830
there's a housing type
which it generates as well.

00:00:53.830 --> 00:00:59.130
And this is just a little
sketch of some of the work

00:00:59.130 --> 00:01:02.690
